import React from 'react'
import { Router, Scene } from 'react-native-router-flux'
import OrderMain from './Orders/OrderMain.js'
import Order from './Orders/Order.js'

const Routes = () => (
   <Router>
      <Scene key = "root">
         <Scene key = "orderMain" component = {OrderMain} title = "订单" initial={true}/>
         <Scene key = "order" component = {Order} title = "上门服务" />
      </Scene>
   </Router>
)
export default Routes
